Results.ReviewText: I only drink decaff coffee and since Nescafe stopped selling Alta Rica Decaff (naughty Nescafe), I went back to Gold Blend decaff. I had forgotten how good it tastes - almost as good as the Alta Rica Decaff. And now available in refill pouches, which saves me money and helps make me feel good about the environment.
Results.Title: Saves money, saves the environment, tastes great

Results.ReviewText: Good value in the refill pack.  Gold blend is my go to decaff instant coffee.  I like coffee but can't do the caffeine, this decaff gives me great taste without the caffeine unlike many decaffs which have no flavour.  Still miss the Alta Rica decaff though.
Results.Title: Great tasting decaff instant, refill value pack

Results.ReviewText: I love coffee but find the caffeine really gives me a headache, so often have to avoid it but with Nescafe Gold blend decaff I can enjoy a delicious rich cup of coffee that tastes just as good as the original!I absolutely love it!
Results.Title: Wonderful Taste, No headache!

Results.ReviewText: This really is the best tasting decaff and it smells so good. It's environmentally friendly packaging show's Nescafe's commitment to helping save our planet
Results.Title: Best on the market

Results.ReviewText: I like the refill pouch idea, all coffee should come in one. Had a great aroma when I open the packet, strong and rich tasting, and very god decaff
Results.Title: Flavoursome & Rich

Results.ReviewText: Love my decaf refill. If it wasn't for this I would have to do without my coffee as the caffeine keeps me awake.☕
Results.Title: My Saviour

Results.ReviewText: This coffee has all the taste without the caffeine and bought as a refill it is cheaper and saves jars
Results.Title: Great taste without the caffeine

Results.Description: A well-rounded, smooth coffee with a rich aroma.
Results.Name: NESCAFÉ GOLD BLEND Instant Coffee
